	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think most or all of the found prototype cartridges were built for testing or showing off.  I'm sure most of the developers had something better, like an EPROM emulator at least.  These companies were putting out big bucks to get carts made, it'd make no sense to use the cheapest tools.  But of course it would vary widely.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
